Kadeem Brown, 25, was killed in the Bronx, New York, on Friday evening .
He slid across the median and hit a bus stop full of waiting passengers .
Driver Emilo Garcia, 44, suffered a seizure moments before the crash .
Police say he continued driving 100 feet or so before crashing into the bus .
Brown died at the scene, while the little girl who was in the cab died a short time later .